<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="12">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-a-yi-74" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-a-yi-74" class="zg-link" title="刘阿一">刘阿一</a></span>
